            <title>[CASSANDRA-8485] Move 2.0 metered flusher to its own thread</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8485</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We are using SS.optionalTasks for the MF right now - something we most definitely should not be doing, given just how important running MF regularly is to the stability of a node. Currently a bunch of other tasks are also using SS.optionalTasks (like serializing caches).&lt;/p&gt;

